1. Always define constant variables in FrameworkConstant class and use it by getters
2. Manage passed,failed,skipped screenshots by property file
3. Retry mechanism is optional,i will suggest to not use same for better ROI.
4. Always declare constant in Uppercase
5. Never Hardcode anything,do it by define variable and use as getter method
6. Listeners-IMethodInterceptor,IAnnotationTransformer,IRetryAnalyzer
7. Use Method chaining approach for better code understanding
8. Mention common methods in Basepage class
9. We are using single DP for all testmethods,Excel to Hashmap
10. If any excel cell is empty,add single quote(') in that cell to avoid NPE
11. When reading integer,decimal from excel cell,append single quote before to convert it to string.